reviewText: Includes the 2000 Sugar Bowl, which makes it that much better than One Team, One Heartbeat. The narrator is great and hearing Gene Deckerhoff with his best sidekick Peter Tom Willis brings a wave of nostalgia to anyone who remembers that magical season.
This video has highligts of all of the 1999 season plus the Title Game.  Great video with great production.  A must have.
